{"tid":1393730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如有老闆決定85罷工 免費送你facebook廣告片一條","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:09:31.000Z","uid":35319,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a31dc291a6623685ed5a7d03407a8ad29e31d5bc","tid":1393730,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"小市民為發聲罷工當然值得支持，<br />\n但最緊要係各大老闆支持。<br />\n如有任何喺香港嘅品牌/商戶/餐廳食肆，<br />\n全職員工達10人以上，<br />\n因為呢個post決定下星期8月5日全公司罷工，<br />\n請喺facebook pm我(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmywaystogetfat%2F&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=f4f45733\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat/</a>)，<br />\n成波之路可略盡綿力免費幫貴公司拍片一條放上成波之路facebook專頁當宣傳之用，<br />\n希望各大老闆支持香港人發聲，<br />\n謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n#雖然好蠢好柒<br />\n#畀唔到乜嘢著數人<br />\n#又諗住引人罷工<br />\n#但我已經諗唔到我仲可以做啲乜嘢<br />\n#或者你地都諗下你地可以做啲乜嘢<br />\n#做管理層或者老闆嘅麻煩都認真諗下<br />\n#唔好問罷一日工有乜嘢用<br />\n#踏得出呢一步先算<br />\n#無一日生意有幾閒<br />\n#試問當香港變成大陸<br />\n#成盤生意都可能無晒<br />\n#跪求原諒我嘅柒<br />\n#剩返幾日無辦法唔急"},{"pid":"bab0b602dba5fb55a7bf148d915a5c7f0b2bb5f8","tid":1393730,"uid":283444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0d2ed17568230b697cea25b9a7d7897c1acde0c","tid":1393730,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"554e6282786f4948c8701d928dd432df61c168ff","tid":1393730,"uid":241869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f37f5c1fca5620b70b0d33dff7d13f2f00b308e5","tid":1393730,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c3625b84e37ec183ac6b68a77eba643b524e70a0","tid":1393730,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28125914